			if {돈::%uuid of player%} >= 200:
				give 1 leather chestplate named "&7낡은 가죽갑옷" to player
				send "&7<&e시스템&7> &a성공적으로 아이템을 구매하셨습니다"
				play sound "minecraft:entity.arrow.hit_player" to player
