	if inventory name is "&a음식상점":
		cancel event
		if clicked slot is 20:
			if {돈::%uuid of player%} >= 5:
				give 1 cookie to player
				send "&7<&e시스템&7> &a성공적으로 아이템을 구매하셨습니다"
